1.  Challenge1 - Terraform (IaC) has been used to create a sample 3 tier architecture.

2. Challenge2 - Shell script is used developed script in order to query the meta data of an instance within aws.
   Below is the syntax to run procedure
   
   scenario 1 : $ sh  challenge2.sh    
               (It will return instance metadeta in json format)

   scenario 2 : $ sh  challenge2.sh  <data key>
                (It will return repective value of the given <data key>)
                
                e.g. :
                $ sh challenge2.sh  region
                $ eu-west-2

3. Challenge3 - Javascript is used to write scriot in order to key value in a nested object function.
                e.g : 
                $ node challenge3.js
                

           